abstract: Soccer Roundup; Manchester United defeats Crystal Palace, 2-1; other soccer matches and news noted.
lead_paragraph: Marouane Fellaini headed in a late winner as Manchester United beat Crystal Palace, 2-1, on Saturday in the English Premier League and moved closer to a return to the Champions League.

headline.main: Late Header Lifts United to First Win in 4 Games
